<item chapterid="611164" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1959" articlename="凰权" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521903209" lastupdate="1521903209" chaptername="第七十章省亲" chapterorder="69" size="8104" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    南明国皇宫，一派歌舞升平，热闹繁华的景象。

